snippet.title: Infinitode 2 English Trailer
snippet.description:
Infinitode 2 is a free, ultimate Tower Defense for Android, desktop PC and iOS, where you can enjoy endless levels with lots of different towers, heaps of loot, mining, crafting, huge upgrade tree and map editor.

Download for Android (free):
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.prineside.tdi2

Join us in social networks:
https://www.facebook.com/infinitodegame
https://discord.gg/4kZ2TJ4
